juisynth.logic

Class Patch

  • java.lang.Object
    • juisynth.logic.Patch

  • public class Patch
extends Object
    Patch contains the settings for the implementation of a synthesizer component, specified as containing an oscillator, a spectrum filter and an ADSR envelope.
    Author:
    juicyp
